=item B<_story_link_edit_and_preview>

 _story_link_edit_and_preview topic story_id

Shows links to edit and preview a story.
=cut
<li>
{-if|{-is_future_story|$0|$1}|<em>|}
<a href='{-l|EDIT_STORY|topic=$0|id=$1}'>{-story_date|%d/%m/%y|$0|$1} - {-story_title|$0|$1}</a>
{-if|{-is_future_story|$0|$1}|</em>|}
<small><a href='{-l|STORY|topic=$0|id=$1}'>[Preview]</a></small>
</li>
